<a href=\"http:\/\/wikipedia.org\">Wikipedia<\/a>.\u00a0\u00a0 Newspapers are dying out in America &#8211; but this example shows why such high-profile companies can not hand the keys to the car to just everyone asking.\u00a0\u00a0 Citizen media has its place, but old media shouldn&#8217;t be attempting to tag it on without understanding the consequences or the work involved in maintaining it.<\/p>\n<p>I wonder if anyone got fired?<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Picture from here A couple of news sources are reporting today (here, here, and here) that the LA Times is suspending its program of using a wiki for editorials.\u00a0\u00a0 Now in a controlled environment like &hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":97591,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[2],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/10.10.2.102\/creevacom\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3901"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/10.10.2.102\/creevacom\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/10.10.2.102\/creevacom\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/10.10.2.102\/creevacom\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/10.10.2.102\/creevacom\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3901"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/10.10.2.102\/creevacom\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3901\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/10.10.2.102\/creevacom\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/97591"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/10.10.2.102\/creevacom\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3901"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/10.10.2.102\/creevacom\/index.php\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=3901"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/10.10.2.102\/cr